      <title>特朗普连续第二个月支出超过筹资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-raised-160-million-but-spent-more-in-race-against-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的竞选活动连续第二个月支出超过筹集的资金，共和党候选人难以跟上民主党人卡马拉·哈里斯强劲的筹款行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/trump-raised-160-million-but-spent-more-in-race-against-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
